      "source": [
        "9)A music streaming application stores songs in the order they are added.\n",
        "Requirements:\n",
        "• Add a new song at the end.\n",
        "• Display the playlist.\n",
        "• Delete a song by title.\n",
        "Tasks:\n",
        "• Explain why Singly Linked List is suitable.\n",
        "• Write Python code for the required operations.\n",
        "• Analyze the time complexity of each operation.\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "raw",
      "id": "1e941b7d-7a27-4ab4-acfb-ac7af5de01f0",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "class Node:\n",
        "    def __init__(self, title):\n",
        "        self.title = title\n",
        "        self.next = None\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "class Playlist:\n",
        "    def __init__(self):\n",
        "        self.head = None\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Add a new song\n",
        "    def add_song(self, title):\n",
        "        new_node = Node(title)\n",
        "\n",
        "        if self.head is None:\n",
        "            self.head = new_node\n",
        "        else:\n",
        "            current = self.head\n",
        "            while current.next is not None:\n",
        "                current = current.next\n",
        "            current.next = new_node\n",
        "\n",
        "        print(f\"{title} added to playlist\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Display the entire playlist\n",
        "    def display(self):\n",
        "        if self.head is None:\n",
        "            print(\"Playlist is empty.\")\n",
        "            return\n",
        "\n",
        "        current = self.head\n",
        "        position = 1\n",
        "\n",
        "        while current is not None:\n",
        "            print(f\"{position}. {current.title}\")\n",
        "            current = current.next\n",
        "            position += 1\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Delete a song by title\n",
        "    def delete_song(self, title):\n",
        "        if self.head is None:\n",
        "            print(\"Playlist is empty.\")\n",
        "            return\n",
        "\n",
        "        if self.head.title == title:\n",
        "            self.head = self.head.next\n",
        "            print(\"Item deleted\")\n",
        "            return\n",
        "\n",
        "        current = self.head\n",
        "\n",
        "        while current.next is not None:\n",
        "            if current.next.title == title:\n",
        "                current.next = current.next.next\n",
        "                print(\"Item deleted\")\n",
        "                return\n",
        "            current = current.next\n",
        "\n",
        "        print(\"Item not found\")\n"
      ]
    },
